2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper focuses on the secure transmission of information in the presence of an eavesdropper, which is a key concern in cryptography and security. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the multiple input multiple output (MIMO) wiretap channel, which is a common model in multimedia communication systems. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper may be relevant to the study of secure communication in social and information networks. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper may be relevant to the design and analysis of secure wireless communication networks.
